Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉安定下来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我们龙骑兵被赋予的唯一使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人是不可能捕获龙之转矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个时候没有被强制转移的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经把那家伙捕获住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩还保持着自己的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不谨慎接触的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把那个捕获住的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个拉库利玛需要龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么 红秧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛会变成什么样 和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起活下去 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了哦 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气也很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进展么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我收拾一下储藏室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储藏室?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一个人是搬不起重物的 不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的12岁的暑假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为明年就要13岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这个暑假你应该尽情的做你喜欢想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么特别想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好享受儿提时代怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试结束以后 我会想怎么玩就怎么玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是摄影机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你出生的时候 爸爸买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还挺贵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得哪里不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的爸爸和妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在才办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚的时候花钱花的太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妈妈决定不办了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在才要举办仪式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好罗曼蒂克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸妈妈直到现在感情还很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊 一直都是很嗯爱的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是爱的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很适合礼服 在结婚式上大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊 一直都很温柔而且漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是这样 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不举行仪式的真正的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是爱的妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是高中生时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好像不知道这事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好帅啊 爱的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不让你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤 那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好像专家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看上去是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑会用么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我说后藤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的结婚仪式 要不要来做摄影师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的结婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的妈妈和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到拍摄的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帅啊 摄影师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在么 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 五
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个团体都到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到试验船这么快就到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是筱原君早就安排好的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备将绝临的调查结果从一开始就置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那只是为了让计划顺利进行而利用的方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现在这个量子反应还在加剧异常变动的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还启动Magic Circle计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的"人类的傲慢毁灭人类自身"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓傲慢是说  现在生存着的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是大人的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的我们 却是在破坏着孩子们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥的力量也许在加速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让那孩子和时空接触的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所看到的不可思议的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是香格里拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个时候开始 就能看见那些人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不过也不能说是人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香格里拉么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是想见我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“来香格里拉吧” 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着假面的男人么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零点的出现率显著提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许和这个有关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空 也许香格里拉的侵蚀已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标确定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注射开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五 四 三 二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是能看见什么 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能看见什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有观测那个坐标的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见反而是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测者一个接一个自毁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空的正在加速歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经到达极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点捕获龙之转矩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了一个罕见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口红？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你一起去找可以共同活下去的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被从选民居住地流放到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让龙之转矩和鸦逃走的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有把你消灭是指导部的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该感到感谢 阿玛米克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错误伤害到他们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去纠正这个错误难道是不可以的么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了让拉库利玛存在下去才战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被束缚在过去而失去了未来可能性的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回顾过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被赋予了那样的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们模拟出来的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只不过是由量子旋转产生的能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也能被认为是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只不过是由于我们的存在干涉的结果而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我这样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那个孩子 遥所认知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子认知到了我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 因为那家伙的存在 鸦和枭才会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而枭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打倒鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和他做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老累啊 真土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙好烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也小气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姐姐 脚碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向老奶奶道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪里的中学的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 她说她是小学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 我们被太过于小觊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被小觊的话 就好好遵守礼仪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐们一起去散步吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 长谷部？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小瞧我们 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微来疼一下你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 长谷部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊 这些姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不会吧 都是美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 我是这家伙的同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐们都是哪个学校的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超~耀眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼福 眼福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这个奇怪的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 眼福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像2班的藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是弟弟什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 笑过头了 力气都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙超级恶劣的 很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是因为她们态度恶劣而多管闲事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 也要看看对象么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 你也是不可能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然把我当傻瓜了 可她们的传闻我还是听过的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那些家伙太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就会有谁来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要在那种家伙的面前哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 擦擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好脏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 还不是擦了 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是应该的么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑枭的灵子能长眠在一个美丽的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场的异常范围还在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是时空间的干涉变的强烈的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看上去是这么平静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕鸦的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只不过是近似值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有正确的表示出我的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无限接近 不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我所长大的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常残酷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个时候的事情已经几乎都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波动…这个时空正在歪曲 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要不失礼 保持礼节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 这样的打扮没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面奇怪吗 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 让人向往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊 遥 不愧是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 真让人不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 力量增强了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只能看到小孩的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是高密度的能量收缩体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能抑制住幻想程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也是未来人么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要和鸦战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让鸦再和谁战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要把你这混蛋碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你战斗也是无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死枭的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样 我还是要消灭你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就和我战斗吧 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不朝着我攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和现在的你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被过去的幻影所束缚背叛同伴的卑鄙者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:20:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使消灭了我和鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能拯救拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能阻止香格里拉的侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩所拥有的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了那些所存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是为了复活这整个歪曲的时空才被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之所以找到龙之转矩 并不是偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 小鹭是消灭不了鸦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己坦诚一些比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还原了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 回拉库利玛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道 一直维持着切断电缆的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来总有一天你自身会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返航
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.95,0:24:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.97,0:24:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说 那个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.77,0:25:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 崩溃吧 消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.54,0:25:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.77,0:25:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所存在的世界是现实吗
